These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, pomegranate, raspberry, cherry, carrot, garlic, lime
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar, bongani, vegafina, swisher, aristoff, siglo
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, french, indonesian, mexican, canadian, colombian, british
City: rome, venice, miami, hamburg, edinburgh, boston, london
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the dutch##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is the canadian##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the french##1
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person eating garlic is in the middle##1
12. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
13. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
14. the colombian is on the left of the indonesian##1
15. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
16. the canadian is on the left of the colombian##1
17. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
18. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the mexican##1
19. the person traveling to miami is in the middle##1
20. the mexican is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
21. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
